<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
 <head>
 <meta charset="UTF-8">
 <title>
 Access Blocked
 </title>
 <style>
 body {
 font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
 background-color: #fff;
 /* White Background */
 color: #333;
 text-align: center;
 padding: 50px;
 }
 .warning {
 color: #2469aa;
 /* Warm Blue */
 font-size: 24px;
 font-weight: bold;
 }
 .container {
 border: 2px solid #2469aa;
 /* Warm Blue Border */
 padding: 20px;
 border-radius: 8px;
 display: inline-block;
 text-align: left;
 background-color: #fff;
 /* White background inside box */
 }
 a {
 color: #2469aa;
 /* Warm Blue */
 text-decoration: none;
 }
 input, textarea {
 width: 100%;
 padding: 8px;
 margin: 5px 0;
 border: 1px solid #2469aa;
 /* Warm Blue Border */
 border-radius: 4px;
 }
 button {
 background-color: #2469aa;
 /* Warm Blue */
 color: white;
 padding: 10px 20px;
 border: none;
 border-radius: 4px;
 cursor: pointer;
 }
 button:hover {
 background-color: #2469aa;
 /* Slightly Darker Warm Blue */
 }
 .logo {
 margin-bottom: 30px;
 }
 .logo img {
 width: 250px;
 /* Increased logo size */
 height: auto;
 }
 
 table {
 width: 100%;
 }
 tr {
 margin-bottom: 30px; /* Added vertical spacing between rows */
 }
 td {
 padding: 4px 0; /* Vertical padding for content inside the cells */
 }
 </style>
 </head>
 <body>
 <div class="logo">
 <img src="https://d3aswa4nvo33j8.cloudfront.net/e/8/e823d0e293982eb63f7718a652ca3d94ea2ca9ba9d45b36775c8728cf98e002136562b23a7bff5439904eb57f837857bf2a47824858b2e9e3f5e75480ec5f461.png" alt="Logo">
 </div>
 <div class="container">
 <p class="warning">
 ⚠️ This site is blocked due to violation of alfanar Internet usage policy ⚠️
 </p>
 <P>
 
 <strong>
 Web Page Blocked 
 </strong>
 
 </P>
 <table>
 <tbody>
 <tr>
 <td>
 <strong>
 Category
 </strong>
 </td>
 <td>
 DomainThreat-WEB
 </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 <td>
 <strong>
 URL
 </strong>
 </td>
 <td>
 https://raw.githubusercontent.com/
 </td>
 </tr>
 </tbody>
 </table>
 
 </p>
 <p>
 Access to the site 
 <strong>
 https://raw.githubusercontent.com/
 </strong>
 has been blocked in accordance with alfanar Internet Security Policy.
 </p>
 <p>
 If you are unable to connect to the internet or facing browsing issues, please contact 
 <a href="mailto:Network_Security@alfanar.com">
